帶同三對球鞋，及後關員表露身份，被告即時逃跑。</span>鄭姓關員捉住被告，惟被告在屢次警告下仍掙扎，其後有四名關員合力制服被告，包括馮姓關員按住被告雙手。惟被告不肯就犯，繼續掙扎，警告下仍強烈抵抗，最後被鎖上手銬制服。三名海關分別手腕、前臂及肩膊受傷。<br />\n<br />\n開頭就話唔清楚係咪冒牌<br />\n但一見到海關就識得逃走<br />\n咁即係知定唔知呀？"},{"pid":"8a993d8d904e9502b5e31db2ccd3962f6a05627a","tid":2096813,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"香港法律 受英國古羅馬法影響 <br />\n功不低過 參考十二銅表法"},{"pid":"be1199a93bc21b5868f6a075b9e823dd9063b04d","tid":2096813,"uid":86509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"75a2fd3022b8f7771bbe8c83013eeb6fa681fc61","tid":2096813,"uid":75767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"On9 差佬有收人工架 講到好似bonus咁 屌你老母真係痴撚線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Aua48Z-vDRXUFaZLGh5YdJ9GXsM=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/4UG5FMLQJZVNGUDTURBNGHNEWA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAua48Z-vDRXUFaZLGh5YdJ9GXsM%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F4UG5FMLQJZVNGUDTURBNGHNEWA.png&h=db7ebc41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fde5cb573d3468a6a223b3cda204ff3c39ee9af7","tid":2096813,"uid":7008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"執法者不受法律限制<br />\n休班也是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23504ff2170e0e9c1e55ee6fd7c1763e8a00495a","tid":2096813,"uid":237209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c18eb6a0bbea51e82b7371dcd0fefa8350de07ac","tid":2096813,"uid":29093,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"賣假貨  拒捕  打公職人員<br />\n<br />\n睇住嚟 3 樣野做齊       又唔駛坐監"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"技能卡「驚謊」<br />\n無視以上一切罪行"},{"pid":"44167042b964c724286ba01cd6bd9c549b884b49","tid":2096813,"uid":1847